Package com.ibm.team.interop.client.rest

Interface Summary
IInteropAdminRestClient Client library interface for the Interop administrative REST service.
IInteropConnectionFactory Interface for creating connections to servers.
IInteropContent Class representing content that has been uploaded to the Jazz repository.
IInteropRestClient Client library interface for the Interop REST service.
IInteropRestClient.IAuthenticator Authenticator callback which must be provided by clients.
IRestExternalProxy Class to represent an ExternalProxy object.
IRestExternalRepositoryConnection Class to represent an ExternalRepositoryConnection object that is marshaled via the Interop REST service.
IRestExternalState Class to represent an ExternalState object.
IRestPropertyMapping Class to represent a PropertyMapping object in a SyncRule.
IRestSyncRule Class to represent a SyncRule object.
 

Exception Summary
InteropClientException Thrown on any error encountered by the interop client services.
InteropNotLicensedException Exception thrown when the client is not licensed to perform Interop operations.
